"{\"uid\": \"myjoyonline.com-paris-2024-cadman-yamoah-eyes-olympics-spot\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Audio By Carbonatix African Games high jump champion Cadman Evans Yamoah reckons winning the gold medal at the continental event is a stepping stone towards greatness and has set sights on reaching new heights.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Carbonatix African Games\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 33}, {\"ngram\": \"Cadman Evans Yamoah\", \"from\": 53, \"to\": 72}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 103}, {\"ngram\": \"the continental event\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 128}, {\"ngram\": \"a stepping stone\", \"from\": 132, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"greatness\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 166}, {\"ngram\": \"sights\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 185}, {\"ngram\": \"new heights\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to JoySports, he describes the success as an honour.\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"JoySports\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"an honour\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel honoured,\\\" Cadman reflects.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cadman\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every athlete needs a stepping stone, and this is just my stepping stone,\\\" he noted.\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every athlete\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 326}, {\"ngram\": \"a stepping stone\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"just my stepping stone\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With his recent triumph at the African Championships, clearing a height of 2.23 meters, Cadman knows that the journey has only just begun.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his recent triumph\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"the African Championships\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 451}, {\"ngram\": \"a height\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"2.23 meters\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"Cadman\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone is trying to qualify for the Olympics,\\\" he remarks.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having achieved this height, a new personal record, I am going back to the drawing board to reset our minds and rechannel our focus.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this height\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"the drawing board\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"our minds\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"our focus\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Those 2.15 or 2.16m bars, we are not focusing on that again,\\\" Cadman states.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are going to practice with 2.25 or 2.35 meters.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2.35 meters\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I had not achieved the 2.23m, probably 2.21m would have been my mark.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2.23m\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"my mark\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's where I would have started my jumps from, so 2.23m is an opening.\\\"\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my jumps\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"2.23m\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"an opening\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With each training session, Cadman pushes himself beyond his limits, determined to soar higher than ever before.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each training session\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1042}, {\"ngram\": \"Cadman\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"his limits\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The track becomes his sanctuary, the bar his ultimate challenge, and the cheers of the crowd fuel his spirit.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The track\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"his sanctuary\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"his ultimate challenge\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"the cheers\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"his spirit\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympic trials draw near, Cadman remains undeterred.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"Cadman\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows that success is not measured by the medals around his neck but by the relentless pursuit of excellence.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"his neck\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"the relentless pursuit\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With each jump, he defies gravity and transcends expectations, a true champion in every sense of the word.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [], \